=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁買左2年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我覺得守豬仲穩陣"},{"pid":"3b076c831d22714828c98b121031c9c805544d64","tid":336943,"uid":48623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:10:13.000Z","msg":"你咁買同倒錢落海有咩分別，唔係話無可能中，你自問係咪超好運個類人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之前馬會公開過有關數據，中頭二三獎既得好小部分人既單買廿蚊（兩注）。<br />\n我自己就一個月買兩次，每次用五百至一千買，買複式。咁耐以來中過一次二獎，兩三次三獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n另外你真係咁想中都有方法，之前有報紙介紹個有人計過點樣最平方法買又肯定中最小三個字既，你搵下啦，但好似要兩三千，搏唔搏就自己決定。"},{"pid":"f5c57224b202f821e4f4a611b4ae6204b40ae54d","tid":336943,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:12:24.000Z","msg":"4條飛 一次買廿期 買左好耐<br />\n成日都中返幾舊水 回本都有試過"},{"pid":"09520f8858b797f0077e4a8d5d240a46b920b65f","tid":336943,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:18:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>4條飛 一次買廿期 買左好耐<br />\n成日都中返幾舊水 回本都有試過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 試過公司每人夾一舊買11個字互串，派左我去買中得一個字比同事屌死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60dc2c742096d8b7288bbcc9a9924ee836201a96","tid":336943,"uid":64047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"可唔可以用kickstarter 搵100個人<br />\nmark定45個號碼每條買9個字(即係5注復式)<br />\n<br />\n然後用呢一set買10期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4785d6888469711904f1cdeb7cb030177563afb1","tid":336943,"uid":63202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google Search 亞米露</blockquote><br />\n屌你老味 冇人理我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b15f39b1773c5571ff36d60412323c4f1ce7d3f","tid":336943,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你咁買同倒錢落海有咩分別，唔係話無可能中，你自問係咪超好運個類人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，之前馬會公開過有關數據，中頭二三獎既得好小部分人既單買廿蚊（兩注）。<br />\n我自己就一個月買兩次，每次用五百至一千買，買複式。咁耐以來中過一次二獎，兩三次三獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n另外你真係咁想中都有方法，之前有報紙介紹個有人計過點樣最平方法買又肯定中最小三個字既，你搵下啦，但好似要兩三千，搏唔搏就自己決定。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n信數據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 5蚊注7個字會唔會好少少？"},{"pid":"47f001c70daf7fa4bfa731d4222800f8737ba4fd","tid":336943,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"買死同一組數字，好間唔中之買<br />\n<br />\n果組數字中過一次640<br />\n<br />\n其餘近半年中過3-4次安慰獎，但我通常買5-6注先有一注中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ddd56823a27e290108065a67642e13e146761a0","tid":336943,"uid":125470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T03:49:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買死同一組數字，好間唔中之買<br />\n<br />\n果組數字中過一次640<br />\n<br />\n其餘近半年中過3-4次安慰獎，但我通常買5-6注先有一注中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n強運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42ae2891c2ed190efdb76fc69e20b8b3b995121f","tid":336943,"uid":82856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"3年20$注 你諗下唔買 拎好洗好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"180346436e1d2b55fc67d4c795e16461e9774f91","tid":336943,"uid":82856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T04:15:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>3年20$注 你諗下唔買 拎<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好</span>洗好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n去"},{"pid":"283616b1d99f006d4fe5848ed53a93400e1bebf7","tid":336